text: Nour Zamen Zammouri (born 1 December 1997 in Djerba; ) is a Tunisian football player. He plays as a Central Defender for Club Sportif Sfaxien (CSS). ==Honours and Achievements== === Club Sportif Sfaxien === * Tunisian Cup (2). == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Tunisian footballers Category:Sportspeople from Tunis
